Are you currently taking any medications or receiving any medical treatments that could reduce or lower the response of your immune system? These medications and treatments can sometimes be called immunosuppressants.


These medications and treatments could be:
  • chemotherapy or radiation
  • high dose steroids like prednisone or dexamethasone
  • immunosuppressants or inhibitors like cyclosporine or tacrolimus
  • biologic therapy like infliximab or remicade
